high_descs: Turn to the left and face the white table
Pick up the butter knife sitting behind the lettuce from the table
Turn around and walk straight to the refrigerator and open the door
Slice a potato in the refrigerator
Turn left and walk straight then turn left again and face the counter with the toaster
Open the cabinet below and put the knife in the bowl
Turn to the left and walk straight then turn left and face the refrigerator
Open the fridge door and remove a slice of potato then close the door
Turn left and walk straight then turn left again and face the counter with the toaster
Open the cabinet below and put the slice in the bowl with the knife
Pick up the bowl with the knife and potato slice inside
Turn to the left walk straight then turn right and face the white table
Set the bowl on the back left of the white table with the knife and slice inside
anns.task_desc: Collect a knife, slice a chilled potato followed by putting in a bowl

high_descs: TUrn to the left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cut the potato in the fridge into slices.
Turn left and walk across the room then turn left to face the cabinet under the coffee maker.
Place the knife in a bowl in the cabinet under the coffee maker and leave the cabinet open.
Turn left and walk across the room and turn left to face the fridge.
Take a slice of potato from inside the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left to face the open cabinet.
Place the potato slice in the bowl with the knife in the cabinet.
Pick up the bowl with the knife and potato slice in it.
Turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the table.
Place the bowl with the knife and potato slice in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife plus a potato slice in a bowl and put it on the long table in the kitchen.

high_descs: Turn left and face the white table on the left
Grab the small knife off of the white table
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cut the egg in the fridge in half
Turn around and go to the coffee maker
Put the knife in the bowl in the cabinet that's underneath the counter
Turn around and go to the fridge
Grab one of the egg slices out of the fridge
Turn around and go to the coffee maker
Put the egg in the bowl in the cabinet that's underneath the counter
Grab the bowl out of the cabinet
Turn left and go to the white table
Place the bowl down on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a bowl with a knife and egg slice in it on the white table
